An established and respected UAE company is looking to enter the events market and launch a number of B2B events over the next 3 years. The company is looking for an individual to oversee and manage its expansion in this field
The candidate must:
Be prepared to locate to the UAE
Have a proven track record of launching and managing B2B events.
Have a proven track record of managing a team
Had some experience in 'creative' events (design etc)
Reporting directly to the CEO, this is an exciting position that has unlimited opportunities to expand in this rapidly growing market.
The right candidate will be able to demonstrate strong interpersonal skills with an entrepreneurial spirit
